  Task 6 ==>
  
  gsutil cp -r gs://cloud-training/gsp321/wp-k8s .
  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  cd wp-k8s
  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
